E4Plus1.uk.description: Marge and Lisa debate a feminist ideal. Beauty, brains AND power: illusion or real? Can those three things be combined? Seeking insight from history, what do they find? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: When a nearby economy is all out of luck, men head to Springfield looking for work. An honest day's work for an honest day's pay? Not if Mayor Quimby can keep them away. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Due to his terrible self-worth, Raj vows to give women a wide berth. Penny tries to teach Sheldon - which is no easy feat. We hope you enjoy this Big Bang repeat. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Leonard, Sheldon and Howard talk science. Will they be met with some defiance? Raj plans a date to help Lucy's fears; let's hope this one won't end in tears. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: When Phil and Claire are caught in bed, their kids are filled with nothing but dread. Jay and Gloria send an email, but to the wrong person. Epic fail! #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: To make sure they don't become boring, Claire and Phil have new bed plans that don't involve snoring. And Jay's got a surprise in store, but executing it becomes a chore. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Howard hurls the first pitch at a baseball game, but will his throw just bring him shame? And Sheldon makes a hefty remark; Penny and Leonard think he's missed the mark. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will the guys invest in Stuart's shop; or will their girlfriends throw a strop? From Penny, Emily keeps her distance; how long can she ignore her existence? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Penny's accused of spoiling the fun, but she's got to get her revision done. The guys try to invent something that's new, but nothing they do leads to a breakthrough. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sheldon and Raj test if they'd cope in a mine. Will they both make it out fine? Penny and Leonard worry about cash, as Penny's gesture meets a backlash. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Captain Holt has had his pie taken. It's enough to leave anyone shaken. Track it down he must. The filling and crust. But who did this dastardly break-in? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Jeffords, Peralta and Diaz have a mission, to find out who stole Parlov's fiction. The rest of the squad take a forensics programme; but Boyle's mouth lands him in a jam. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Simpsons don't want to leave their cruise, so Bart comes up with a clever ruse. He starts pretending, that the world is ending. Oh no, what terrible news... #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: With the help of a rather dashing, crime-fighting spy, can Homer be a better husband? Well, he'll give it a try... #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: It's time to get intimate and go deep, for some it's awks, others a big leap. Time to lay it bare, nothing to hide, but interference makes some pairs collide. #NationalPoetryDay (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sheldon applies pressure for a wedding date. But Penny and Leonard want to wait. Raj has a wobble. Will it lead to a squabble? All as Amy re-evaluates. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: A confession leaves Penny in shock, as Leonard says he's run amok. And Sheldon feels utter heartache, when Amy puts their relationship on a break. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart learns he made loads of cash as a baby ad star, but much to his frustration; it turns out Homer's spent it all, so Bart files for emancipation. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Homer tours the country on the trail of a special burger. Lisa joins a spelling bee but the competition's murder. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: What unlikely events lead to Lisa going undercover as a nun? I think it's something to do with Marge looking straight at the sun. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Krusty'll never know if his dead dad approves of his legacy. Lisa's very worried about Homer's life expectancy. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates: Valentine's
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will twins find blokes with va va voom, in our so-romantic dining room?  And can Roisin from Ireland bring a love thang, for bar manager Saskia who loves a Gaelic twang? #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: The dinner party serves up romantic confessions, with a side order of tricky questions. Can a bride get her validation, or will it be a red flag illumination? #NationalPoetryDay (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: A cosy throwback to 2021, for some Gogglebox moments, but what was on? Can't remember? Leave it to our critics, to see what they think about telly's best picks. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Naked Attraction
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sex toy tester Hayley wants a buzz. Finding love too? We hope that she does! Dmitri climbs up trees with his chopper. Can he find love? We hope he won't come a cropper. #NationalPoetryDay

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Romantic confessions are on the menu at the second dinner party, and one bride questions her marriage when she struggles to find validation from her husband. (S10 Ep10) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Rick and Morty [adult swim]
E4Plus1.uk.description: Childrick of Mort: Rick, Morty, Beth, Summer and Jerry share a family vacation kind of galactic adventure. What could possibly go wrong? (S4 Ep9/10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Robot Chicken: Self-Discovery
E4Plus1.uk.description: Special: The Robot Chicken Nerd embarks on a journey of self-discovery by going on reality shows! Will he find a 90 Day Fiancé? Or will he wind up as Shark Week chum?

E4Plus1.uk.title: Below Deck
E4Plus1.uk.description: Disappointing Daddy: Barbie must decide whether to honour her family's expectations or follow her heart with Kyle. Chef Nick gets some unexpected pushback. (S11 Ep14/17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Special Edna (a.k.a. Love and Marking): When Skinner stands up Mrs Krabappel to attend to his mother's whims, Bart nominates her for Teacher of the Year. (S14 Ep7/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Dad Who Knew Too Little: Homer hires a detective to spy on Lisa so he can get to know her better. But when Homer doesn't pay him, the detective frames Lisa for a crime. (S14 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Separation Oscillation: Sheldon films a special post-break-up episode of Fun with Flags. Bernadette feels guilty about withholding a secret from Penny. (S9 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Ringmaster Keifth: Cam tries to make up for his Thanksgiving debacle by hosting a New Year feast. And Phil's not sure how to feel about his dad dating his childhood babysitter. (S8 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Sarge & Pea: Cam is incensed when a rude parent robs him of a precious Lily moment during her dance recital. Jay, Claire and Mitch unexpectedly run into Dede at a family wedding. (S8 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Grasshopper Also: In Carlstadt, New Jersey, Gordon Ramsay attempts to save the Grasshopper Also, a family-owned Irish restaurant that's on its last legs. (S4 Ep4) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Grab It!: Jay's favourite place in the world may be losing some of its charm when Phil considers becoming a member. And Claire mistakes her influence on Alex's life choices. (S8 Ep6)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Thanksgiving Jamboree: Phil spares no expense on a Thanksgiving jamboree. And Hayley has to tell her dad that she'd rather spend the holidays with her boyfriend. (S8 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Davide: In Boston, Gordon Ramsay visits Davide, an Italian restaurant that's been run into the ground by brothers Frank and Anthony. Can they learn to trust each other again? (S4 Ep5) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Romantic confessions are on the menu at the second dinner party, and one bride questions her marriage when she struggles to find validation from her husband. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Replaceable You: When Homer loses his job to his eager new assistant, he teams up with Ned to reveal her evil past. (S23 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Ten-Per-Cent Solution: The TV network cancel Krusty the Clown's show. Can his first agent, Annie (Joan Rivers), help him craft a comeback? (S23 Ep8/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Closet Reconfiguration: When Howard and Bernadette get Sheldon to organise their untidy closet, Sheldon finds an unopened letter from Howard's long-absent father. (S6 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tenure Turbulence: Leonard, Sheldon, Raj and Kripke all compete for the same vacancy at the university. (S6 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Princess Party: The guest list for Lily's princess-themed birthday party gets a little out of hand when Mitchell decides to invite Mum, much to Claire's dismay. (S2 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Regrets Only: Phil and Claire have a huge fight but Phil hasn't got a clue what it's about. Gloria and Jay try to help them. (S2 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Misinterpretation Agitation: A smitten doctor turns up at Penny's door after her flirtatious sales techniques for the pharmaceutical company work a little too well. (S8 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Prom Equivalency: The girls decide to re-enact their high school proms with their current partners on the roof of the apartment building. (S8 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Septum Deviation: When Leonard has to have minor surgery on his nose, Sheldon is the one who seems to need sympathy. Raj is upset when his parents split up. (S8 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Champagne Reflection: Sheldon and Amy record the final episode of their internet show Fun with Flags. Penny tells Bernadette how her colleagues really feel about her. (S8 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: 99: The squad go to a funeral in LA, where Holt hears that he's in the running for his dream job: NYPD Commissioner. Meanwhile, Boyle pries into Diaz's personal life. (S5 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Game Night: Diaz begs Peralta to help her break some big news to her parents, but Mr and Mrs Diaz jump to the wrong conclusion. Meanwhile, the squad have internet problems. (S5 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Beyond Blunderdome: Mel Gibson hires Homer to help him rewrite his remake of Mr Smith Goes to Washington. (S11 Ep1/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brother's Little Helper: An experimental ADHD drug improves Bart's behaviour but makes him paranoid: is Major League Baseball using a satellite to read his thoughts? (S11 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: Romantic confessions are on the menu at the second dinner party, and one bride questions her marriage when she struggles to find validation from her husband. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bachelor Party Corrosion: The guys' science skills are tested when they get a flat tyre during Leonard's surprise bachelor party weekend in Mexico. (S9 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The 2003 Approximation: Sheldon sulks when Penny and Leonard announce that they're moving in together. Howard and Raj form a band to play at the comic book shop. (S9 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Star Is Born Again: A famous and sultry movie star (guest star Marisa Tomei) swoops into town with eyes for none other than Ned Flanders, making him the envy of Springfield. (S14 Ep13/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mr Spritz Goes to Washington: Krusty wreaks havoc on the political system after the Simpsons help him to get elected. (S14 Ep14/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: In the Name of the Grandfather: Homer takes the family to Ireland so that Grampa can visit quaint village pub O'Flanagan's one last time. (S20 Ep14/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Wreck of the Relationship: Homer and Bart take part in a father-son therapy exercise on a ship. While they're away, Marge gets involved in Homer's fantasy football league. (S26 Ep2/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Will a gaming nerd finally find her 'geeky James Bond'? Can an actor overcome their First Dates stage nerves? And will an ex-wild thing's tattoos wreck his chances of new love? (S20 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Notting Hill
E4Plus1.uk.description: (1999) Hugh Grant and Julia Roberts star in the BAFTA-winning comedy romance about a bookshop owner who manages to get a glamorous movie star to go out with him. With Rhys Ifans.
